title: I Heart Series - Lindsey Kelk
description:
I Heart New York [I Heart, #1]

Perfect for fans of Sophie Kinsella, get ready for the summer debut of the year...When you're running away from a broken heart, there's only one place to go...Adjusting tiaras at the foot of the aisle, Angela and her best friend prepare for the wedding of the year....

Goodreads Link : http://www.goodreads.com/book/show/6202661-i-heart-new-york


I Heart Hollywood [I Heart, #2]

Celebs, sunshine and beautiful boys...enough to lead a girl astray? Angela Clark can't believe her luck! she's an English girl living in New York with a dream job at hip magazine....

Goodreads Link : http://www.goodreads.com/book/show/6766226-i-heart-hollywood


I Heart Paris [I Heart, #3]

Angela is in the city of love -- but romance is taking a nose-dive! When Angela Clark's boyfriend Alex suggests a trip to Paris at the same time as hip fashion mag Belle asks her to write a piece....

Goodreads Link : http://www.goodreads.com/book/show/7537072-i-heart-paris


I Heart Vegas [I Heart, #4]

Angela Clark loves her life in New York. She loves her job, her friends and her gorgeous musician boyfriend, Alex, who is finally ready to move in with her and start planning their future together....

Goodreads Link : http://www.goodreads.com/book/show/11685242-i-heart-vegas


I Heart London [I Heart, #5]

Home is where the heart is. Right? Angela Clark has fallen in love with America -- and it's starting to love her back. Throw one expired visa into the mix, and things quickly take a turn for the worse....
